data.description: Gated Community in Tuscany Preserve, Beautiful large 2 Story Property. Lots of Space with a large backyard and paver driveway. Beautiful 4 Bed, 2 bath, Clubhouse with Fitness center, Pool, Tennis Courts, Tuscany Preserve is a Gated Community with beautiful Resort Styles Amenities. This four bedroom, two bath features high ceilings, a large master suite with walk in closet; a beautifully appointed kitchen with granite countertops and eat in bar top, and accent lighting under upper cabinets. The kitchen overlooks the great room which offers a great casual, family gathering space. Low monthly HOA dues includes yard maintenance & irrigation, basic cable TV and FREE INTERNET which allows you to take full advantage of resort-style living and the many amenities it offers including Clubhouse, pool, hot tub, state of the art fitness center, tennis and basketball courts Minutes from Lake Marion, a natural preserved lake, boating and water sports in within 5 minutes from two new highways. Call today for your private showing!!!
